{"tid":504003,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"20歲社長教大家如何保護自己","createTime":"2017-12-19T12:47:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-19T16:41:01.000Z","uid":66607,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b7bdd58c6d87771a15cd276fbaa6a38a50f5bde5","tid":504003,"uid":66607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T12:47:40.000Z","msg":"#metoo開始傳到日本，一些名人都發帖分享自己的經歷。例如是AMF有限公司（製作青少年網路節目的公司）的社長椎木里佳。椎木現就讀於慶應大學，高中時代就當社長，所以很多女性都憧憬她。近日，她在Twitter發帖講述受性騷擾的經歷，並教導女性如何保護自己。<br />\n<br />\n椎木里佳社長指，廣告業界有很多人會提出性交易，一旦拒絕就會失去工作上的合作機會。她曾經因為這樣而失望、難過，但她強調絕對不能讓步，出賣自己的身體。不過，即使擁有堅定意志，有些人還是會採取強硬手段，例如是下藥。她說，有一次跟工作上來往的男性吃晚飯，因為對方的風評不太好，所以當晚特別小心行事。當時，男性替她取飲品，高度警戒的椎木只舔了一口，已經有點頭暈，於是馬上回家。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://japhub.com/?c=6676\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fjaphub.com%2F%3Fc%3D6676&d=FWXRXA3W5kmi1UuwQ2ATijCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=89200bc1\" target=\"_blank\">http://japhub.com/?c=6676</a>"},{"pid":"3b3618e57fde8ae3224b526a2dc1737a41976d52","tid":504003,"uid":71092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T12:59:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2379a551efa9d8614dedc427dc98ae1489582d5","tid":504003,"uid":13250,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T13:08:51.000Z","msg":"補返張圖啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/19/210849_a9aaf07e856c9b76dd83415c375c171b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F19%2F210849_a9aaf07e856c9b76dd83415c375c171b.jpg&h=3449d166&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c061352e3751c26fbf6e21b682d8fcb21f8cd268","tid":504003,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T13:10:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"95cb8cdfa28416cd5d40f6c09912cb899027aea5","tid":504003,"uid":402,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T13:12:27.000Z","msg":"就快行過隔離都當你想強姦"},{"pid":"a06331aa9a08bd76d05a9c8910aa8f0f4b64168b","tid":504003,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T13:13:21.000Z","msg":"咁既樣會有人落藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b03a3bce6dee6d1ad72d85c0aa287f3f7456eccd","tid":504003,"uid":52595,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T13:21:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b660a6636a309095dc2b4999a3b990384be50d80","tid":504003,"uid":61462,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T13:34:17.000Z","msg":"#metoo,<br />\n啲鹹濕佬真係好撚恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f24210ba5d0a85dd941ec911496a75517f73689","tid":504003,"uid":70505,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T13:34:28.000Z","msg":"認真好撚靚女，結衣級數"},{"pid":"3cbc63f145efa82e693fa7826fe1bbab93a0d0b3","tid":504003,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T13:37:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68388f220758f63ae2c81d689f93e63f66f609c0","tid":504003,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T16:41:01.000Z","msg":"美女？"}]}